These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
House: tower, cape-cod, wooden, futuristic
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, dahlia, rose
1. the cape-cod house is between the tower house and the person who growsiris##2
2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
3. the cape-cod house is somewhere between the futuristic house and the tower house##7
4. the person who growsiris is in an even position##4
5. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
6. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| House   | wooden | futuristic       | cape-cod | tower        |
| Flower      | dahlia  | iris | rose        | daisy |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
City: miami, new-york, prague, nizza
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, water, mirinda
1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person traveling to prague##7
2. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to miami##5
3. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is between the person drinking water and the person drinking tea##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| City     | prague | new-york       | nizza         | miami     |
| Beverage   | tea   | mirinda | water | hot-chocolate |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, bellflower, lily, amaryllis
House: futuristic, palace, victorian, tower
1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the tower house is somewhere between the palace house and the futuristic house##7
3. the victorian house is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the futuristic house is somewhere between the tower house and the person who growsbellflower##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Flower   | bellflower | amaryllis | lily | poppy  |
| House   | victorian | futuristic  | tower   | palace |

