.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
City: hamburg, new-york, liverpool, rome
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, prince, vegafina, bolivar
1. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person traveling to hamburg is somewhere between the prince-smoker and the person traveling to rome##7
3. the person traveling to liverpool is the bolivar-smoker##1
4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| City   | new-york | hamburg | rome       | liverpool |
| Cigar   | prince      | old-henry   | vegafina | bolivar  |

