.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, van, helicopter, boat
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, police-officer, electrician, project-manager
1. the project-manager is on the left or right of the person driving the van##3
2. the dressmaker is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the project-manager is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person driving the quad-bike##7
5. the project-manager is on the left of the electrician##1
6. the police-officer is somewhere to the left of the project-manager##5
7. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport         | helicopter | quad-bike   | boat | van |
| Job   | dressmaker      | police-officer | project-manager      | electrician |

