2. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
6. the person traveling to colone is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to hamburg##7
7. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is parkour##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Sport      | cycling | lacrosse      | parkour | swimming     |
| City   | edinburgh    | colone | hamburg   | paris |

