.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
House: futuristic, farmhouse, craftsman, ranch-style
4 different pets are kept: frog, rabbit, turtle, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the frog is on the far left##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere between the futuristic house and the craftsman house##7
5. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| House          | ranch-style    | futuristic   | farmhouse | craftsman  |
| Pet   | frog | turtle | guinea-pig    | rabbit |

