3. the modern house is the musician##1
4. the gothic-revival house is somewhere between the modern house and the ranch-style house##7
5. the colonial house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
6. the project-manager is on the right of the musician##1
7. the project-manager is on the left of the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival | colonial | ranch-style |
| Job           | musician   | project-manager    | chef       | firefighter  |

