1. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is somewhere to the left of the person who growssunflower##5
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsdahlia is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person who growsballoon-flower##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Flower   | poppy | dahlia | balloon-flower | sunflower   |
| Hobby   | cooking    | traveling      | dancing      | singing |

