2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
3. the fan disco is not the person traveling to london##6
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the fan ambient##1
5. the fan country is somewhere to the right of the fan indie##5
6. the person traveling to marseilles is somewhere between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to san-francisco##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
