.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, snake, dog, turtle
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, june, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the dog##1
4. the owner of the dog is not the person who's birthday is in january##6
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the owner of the dog##7
7. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Pet       | turtle | lizard | snake | dog |
| Birthday   | march   | november      | january        | june  |

