3. the paramedic is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the firefighter is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the firefighter##1
7. the person who's birthday is in february is the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday      | july   | december | february | march   |
| Job   | videographer | firefighter   | paramedic | photographer |

