.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-16::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, scientific, comedy, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, rowing, biathlon
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the person who's sport is sailing##7
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere between the person who's sport is rowing and the person watching martial-arts movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |    3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts | sports | comedy | scientific  |
| Sport   | sailing     | soccer   | rowing    | biathlon |

