.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-19::.
There 4 different types of food: lime, tomato, cherry, artichoke
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, coffee
1. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
2. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5
4. the person eating artichoke is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking coffee is not the person eating cherry##6
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person eating lime and the person eating cherry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Food   | artichoke | cherry | tomato      | lime |
| Beverage     | coffee  | soy-milk  | hot-chocolate | cola   |

