.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, bolivar, dunhill, montecristo
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, chess, hiking, reading
1. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is cooking and the bolivar-smoker##7
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the dunhill-smoker##5
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Cigar         | bolivar    | dunhill | montecristo     | havana |
| Hobby   | hiking | reading  | chess | cooking |

 